Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Add Stremio Live TV with XMLTV EPG and fix QR LAN IP

- New Live TV tab: channel-only Stremio browser with lazy EPG now-playing
  bars, TV Guide screen, and EPG channel mapping (ported from PlayTorrioV2).
- Settings: XMLTV URL field, Open TV Guide, Match EPG channels; prefs sync
  via existing remote settings JSON.
- QR code URL: detect LAN IP via interfaces and WiFi first; routing socket
  only as last resort; refresh IP on resume and after server start.
